Key Match Events: Gibraltar held Wales to a 0-0 draw, ending Wales' 13-match losing streak
Pre-Game Insights: BBC Sport Wales' X account tweeted that Gibraltar were in the midst of the worst losing streak in their history
Post-Match Reflections: Page was booed following the game and insisted he understood the frustrations of the fans
Miscellaneous Highlights: Gibraltar poked fun at Wales on social media after the game, sharing a meme in response to a BBC Wales post
Others: The match was played at the Estadio Algarve, and Wales fans called for Rob Page to be sacked after the result
